Package LDLinkedList_pkg

Class Like

java.lang.Object
LDLinkedList_pkg.Interaction
LDLinkedList_pkg.Like
public class Like extends Interaction
The Like class represents a user's like on a post on a social media platform. It extends the Interaction class and contains information about the account that made the like.
